SELECT
    TO_CHAR(C_EXEC_TIME, 'HH24') as hour_of_day,
    ROUND(AVG(query_count_per_subscriber), 2) as avg_query_count
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            t.c_ab_ref as subscriber_id,
            TO_CHAR(q.C_EXEC_TIME, 'HH24') as hour_of_day,
            COUNT(q.id) as query_count_per_subscriber
        FROM
            qry_type t
        JOIN
            qry_queue q ON t.id = q.c_qry_type AND q.C_ST = 1
        GROUP BY
            t.c_ab_ref, TO_CHAR(q.C_EXEC_TIME, 'HH24')
    ) sq
GROUP BY
    hour_of_day
ORDER BY
    hour_of_day;

---
- name: Check for tcpdump process
  shell: ps aux | grep tcpdump | grep -v grep
  register: tcpdump_process

- name: Monitoring tcpdump process
  block:

    - name: Wait for 3 seconds
      pause:
        seconds: 3

    - name: Check for tcpdump process
      shell: ps aux | grep tcpdump | grep -v grep
      register: tcpdump_process

  until: tcpdump_process.stdout | length == 0
  retries: 1200
  delay: 0

- name: Include tcpdump.yml if tcpdump is not running
  import_tasks: tcpdump.yml
  when: tcpdump_process.rc != 0

---
- block:

  - name: Check for tcpdump process
    shell: ps aux | grep tcpdump | grep -v grep
    register: tcpdump_process

  - name: Wait for 3 seconds
    pause:
      seconds: 3

  loop: "{{ range(0, 1200)|list }}"
  loop_control:
    extended: yes
  when: tcpdump_process.stdout | length == 0

- name: Include tcpdump.yml if tcpdump is not running
  import_tasks: tcpdump.yml
  when: tcpdump_process.rc != 0

#!/bin/bash

# Prompt the user for their Steam API key
read -p "Enter your Steam API key: " STEAM_API_KEY

# Prompt the user for their Steam user ID
read -p "Enter your Steam user ID: " STEAM_USER_ID

# Loop through each game entry in your .vdf file and add the artwork
while read line; do
    if [[ "$line" =~ \"([0-9]+)\" ]]; then
        GAMEID="${BASH_REMATCH[1]}"
        URL="http://api.steampowered.com/ISteamUserStats/GetSchemaForGame/v2/?key=${STEAM_API_KEY}&appid=${GAMEID}|jq '.game.icon'"
        ICON_URL=$(curl -s "${URL}" | tr -d '"')
        curl -s "${ICON_URL}" > "${HOME}/.steam/steam/games/game_${GAMEID}/header.jpg"
        sed -i "s|\"headerimage\".*|\"headerimage\" \"~/.steam/steam/games/game_${GAMEID}/header.jpg\"|" ~/.steam/steam/steamapps/common/libraryfolders.vdf
    fi
done < ~/.steam/steam/steamapps/libraryfolders.vdf

amigosDe :: RedSocial -> Usuario -> [Usuario]
amigosDe red us = usuariosRelacionados (relaciones red) us

usuariosRelacionados :: [Relacion] -> Usuario -> [Usuario]
usuariosRelacionados [] _ = []
usuariosRelacionados (rel:relaciones) us | fst rel == us = snd rel : usuariosRelacionados relaciones us
                                         | snd rel == us = fst rel : usuariosRelacionados relaciones us
                                         | otherwise     = usuariosRelacionados relaciones us

#!/bin/bash

# Define file paths and names
ref_vol="path/to/reference.nii.gz"
trans_mat="path/to/transformation.mat"
input_vols=("path/to/volume1.nii.gz" "path/to/volume2.nii.gz" "path/to/volume3.nii.gz" "path/to/volume4.nii.gz" "path/to/volume5.nii.gz" "path/to/volume6.nii.gz" "path/to/volume7.nii.gz")
output_dir="path/to/output"

# Run FLIRT for each input volume
for input_vol in "${input_vols[@]}"
do
  # Define output file name
  output_file="$(basename "$input_vol" .nii.gz)_flirt.nii.gz"
  
  # Run FLIRT
  flirt -in "$input_vol" -ref "$ref_vol" -init "$trans_mat" -applyxfm -out "$output_dir/$output_file"
done

#!/bin/bash

offset=0
step=10485760  # 10M，字节数
while true; do
    # 从原始文件中读取10M数据并进行编码转换，输出到stdout
    dd bs=1 if=original_file.txt of=/dev/stdout skip=$offset count=$step \
        2>/dev/null | iconv -f utf-8 -t gbk
    
    # 移动指针到下一个10M位置
    offset=$((offset + step))
    
    # 如果读取到文件结尾则跳出循环
    [ $? -ne 0 ] && break
done

#!/bin/bash
USER="votre_utilisateur_mysql"
PASSWORD="votre_mot_de_passe_mysql"
OUTPUT="/chemin/vers/votre/repertoire/de/sauvegarde"
 
# Créer le dossier de sauvegarde si nécessaire
if [ ! -d $OUTPUT ];
then
    mkdir -p $OUTPUT
fi
 
# Boucle à travers toutes les bases de données et créer une sauvegarde individuelle
databases=`mysql -u $USER -p$PASSWORD -e "SHOW DATABASES;" | grep -Ev "(Database|mysql|performance_schema|information_schema)"`
 
for db in $databases; do
    mysqldump -u $USER -p$PASSWORD --force --opt --events --databases $db | gzip > "$OUTPUT/$db.gz"
done

sel_sort xs = sel_sort' xs

    sel_sort' [] = []
    sel_sort' (x:xs) = let (min, rest) = sel x xs
                       in min : sel_sort' rest

    sel min [] = (min, [])
    sel min (x:xs)
      | x < min   = let (newMin, rest) = sel x xs
                    in (newMin, min : rest)
      | otherwise = let (newMin, rest) = sel min xs
                    in (newMin, x : rest)

#!/bin/bash

src="/source/path"
dest="/destination/path"

find "$src" -type f | while read -r file; do
    base=$(basename -- "$file")
    dest_file="$dest/${base%%.*}-$(date +%s).${base##*.}"
    cp "$file" "$dest_file"
done

SELECT
  strftime('%Y-%m-%d', e_end.timestamp) as day,
  SUM(e_end.timestamp - e_start.timestamp) as total_duration
FROM
  (SELECT
     idcase,
     MIN(timestamp) as timestamp
   FROM events_log
   GROUP BY idcase) as e_start
JOIN
  (SELECT
     idcase,
     MAX(timestamp) as timestamp
   FROM events_log
   GROUP BY idcase) as e_end
ON e_start.idcase = e_end.idcase
GROUP BY day;

#!/bin/bash

# Time to display the notification before hibernation (in seconds)
NOTIFICATION_TIME=10

# The message to be displayed in the notification
NOTIFICATION_MESSAGE="System will hibernate in $NOTIFICATION_TIME seconds. Please save your work."

# Display the notification
notify-send "Hibernation Notice" "$NOTIFICATION_MESSAGE"

# Wait for the specified notification time
sleep "$NOTIFICATION_TIME"

# Check if notify-send process is still running and kill it, to make sure the notification does not show up after hibernation
for pid in $(pgrep notify-send); do
    if [ "${pid}" != "$$" ]; then
        kill "${pid}"
    fi
done

# Initiate hibernation
systemctl hibernate

(defn average-invoice-amount [year]
  (let [year-invoices (invoices-for-year year)]
    (when (seq year-invoices)
      (/ (reduce + 0 (map :amount year-invoices))
         (count year-invoices)))))

async_stmt ::= "async" (funcdef | with_stmt | for_stmt)
if_stmt ::= "if" named_expression ":" suite ( "elif" named_expression ":" suite )* ["else" ":" suite]
while_stmt ::= "while" named_expression ":" suite ["else" ":" suite]
for_stmt ::= "for" targetlist "in" expression_list ":" [TYPE_COMMENT] suite ["else" ":" suite]
try_stmt ::= "try" ":" suite
               ((except_clause ":" suite)+
                ["else" ":" suite]
                ["finally" ":" suite] |
                "finally" ":" suite)
with_stmt ::= "with" with_item ("," with_item)*  ":" [TYPE_COMMENT] suite
with_item ::= expression ["as" target]

selectNApart :: Int -> [e] -> [e]
selectNApart n lst
  | length lst > n = head lst : selectNApart n (drop n lst)
  | not (null lst) = [head lst]
  | otherwise = []

FROM --platform=linux/amd64 amazonlinux:2
WORKDIR /app
COPY . .

# Node.js 설치 및 프로젝트 의존성 설치
# `yum clean all`을 통해 캐시 파일을 정리하고, 하나의 RUN 명령어로 모든 작업을 처리하여 레이어 수를 줄입니다.
RUN yum install -y gcc-c++ make && \
    curl -fsSL https://rpm.nodesource.com/setup_16.x | bash - && \
    yum install -y nodejs && \
    npm install && \
    yum clean all

# 서비스 배포를 위한 CMD 변경
# 혹시 환경 변수가 Docker 이미지 안에 포함되어 커밋되지 않도록 AWS_ACCESS 및 AWS_SECRET은 보통 
# Docker run 시에 -e 옵션을 통해 외부에서 받거나, Docker Swarm이나 Kubernetes 같은 오케스트레이션 도구를 사용하여 관리합니다.
# CMD에 직접적인 환경 변수 파일을 읽는 것 대신, 환경 변수를 직접 주입하는 방식을 추천합니다.
CMD ["bash", "-c", "sls config credentials --provider aws --key $AWS_ACCESS --secret $AWS_SECRET && sls deploy"]

if_statement ::= "if" expression ":" block ["else" ":" block].
block ::= statement {statement}.
statement ::= if_statement | assignment | expression.
assignment ::= identifier "=" expression.
identifier ::= letter {letter | digit}.
letter ::= "a" | ... | "z" | "A" | ... | "Z".

expression: term term_tail
term_tail: '+' term term_tail | '-' term term_tail | epsilon

term: factor factor_tail
factor_tail: '*' factor factor_tail | '/' factor factor_tail | epsilon 

factor: NUMBER | '(' expression ')'

CALCULATE m = sqrt(2b^2 + 2c^2 - a^2)

  V
PRINT m

END
